modules.description: Provides functions to copy text to and retrieve text from the system clipboard. Works with string data types and handles asynchronous operations for clipboard interactions. Enables seamless integration of copy-paste functionality in mobile applications.

Copies a string to the system clipboard with optional success and error callbacks, and retrieves text from the clipboard with a result callback and optional error handling. Operates on strings and callback functions to interact with native clipboard mechanisms. Used to synchronize text data between app components and the operating system's clipboard buffer.
